# Required for the contact form to submit.
# Without this, the submit button is disabled.
#
# Get your form ID:
# 1. Go to https://formspree.io and sign in
# 2. Open your existing form (e.g. the one used by ELK Lark)
# 3. Copy the form ID from the URL: https://formspree.io/f/XXXXX  →  XXXXX is the ID
#
# Create a file named .env in this directory (same folder as package.json) with:
#
VITE_FORMSPREE_FORM_ID=paste_your_form_id_here
#
# Then restart the dev server (npm run dev). The form will POST to Formspree and show the success message.
